<titleabbrev>Developer's Guide</titleabbrev>


<bookinfo><abstract><title>Introduction</title>
<para>
The C Common Libraries provide an abstraction layer for data types, libc system
calls, and data structures used throughout the Globus Toolkit and useful for
applications that use the Globus Toolkit.
</para>
</abstract></bookinfo>

